16:30.057 --> 16:32.725
- And we're on a river.
- Oh, God.

16:32.725 --> 16:35.628
The minnows will
be feasting tonight.

16:35.628 --> 16:38.631
- Are there girls looking?
- Oh, yes.

16:38.631 --> 16:41.634
Every single girl on this deck
is looking at you right now.

16:41.634 --> 16:43.703
It's okay.
He's just vomiting.

16:43.703 --> 16:45.872
Would you like a little bubbly
to settle the tummy?

16:45.872 --> 16:48.508
- No, thank you.
- All right.

16:49.609 --> 16:53.146
Whoa! This yacht is bigger
than my house.

16:58.718 --> 17:01.754
Hey, wanna mess around?

17:01.754 --> 17:04.424
- Now?
- Yeah.

17:06.326 --> 17:09.096
- No, thanks.
- Oh.

17:09.096 --> 17:10.463
Pretty please.

17:13.733 --> 17:14.834
What's wrong?

17:14.834 --> 17:16.536
Nothing.

17:19.639 --> 17:21.774
Come on, tell me.

17:25.678 --> 17:28.981
What's gonna happen to us,
Wheeler?

17:28.981 --> 17:30.817
What do you mean?

17:30.817 --> 17:33.686
I mean, when you go to school.

17:39.192 --> 17:42.229
Nothing. I mean, sure,
it'll be a little tough

17:42.229 --> 17:43.596
that first year
while I'm up there

17:43.596 --> 17:45.265
and you're still here
finishing your degree.

17:45.265 --> 17:49.136
But we'll visit each other
and talk all the time...

17:49.136 --> 17:51.671
and have a ton of phone sex.

17:51.671 --> 17:54.274
Mostly on nights and weekends
when rates are lower.

17:54.274 --> 17:55.675
Mm-hmm.

17:57.144 --> 18:01.448
Until you meet some smart girl
and forget all about me?

18:01.448 --> 18:03.150
It's not gonna happen.

18:19.031 --> 18:21.033
You have to be very quiet.

18:21.033 --> 18:23.670
I'm so quiet, I'm a mouse.

18:58.238 --> 19:00.673
Would the jury
foreman please rise?

19:02.475 --> 19:04.211
Has the jury reached
a unanimous verdict?

19:04.211 --> 19:05.645
We have, Your Honor.

19:19.359 --> 19:21.628
Will the defendant please rise?

19:25.632 --> 19:28.067
On the counts
of insider trading,

19:28.067 --> 19:29.502
securities and mail fraud,

19:29.502 --> 19:32.939
and providing false statements
to the government,

19:32.939 --> 19:34.841
the jury finds Douglas Getty...

19:41.248 --> 19:42.649
Guilty on all counts.

19:44.384 --> 19:47.019
The jury is thanked and excused.

19:47.019 --> 19:49.922
Court is dismissed.

20:12.912 --> 20:15.214
It'll be okay.

20:17.049 --> 20:19.919
It'll all be okay.
It's gonna be okay,
sweetheart.

20:19.919 --> 20:22.021
Okay?

20:22.021 --> 20:23.290
I love you.

20:23.290 --> 20:27.026
I'm gonna take her outside
for some air.

20:27.026 --> 20:29.262
That's a good idea.
Come here.

20:33.266 --> 20:34.534
Okay.

20:36.135 --> 20:37.937
It's okay. It's okay.

20:39.472 --> 20:42.309
- How did you know?
- Know what?

20:43.843 --> 20:46.513
To come today.
How did you know the verdict
was coming down today?

20:48.748 --> 20:50.983
David told me.

20:58.024 --> 20:59.626
It's gonna be okay.

21:11.203 --> 21:12.439
Yeah.

21:23.149 --> 21:27.554
- There he is,
the birthday boy!
- Having fun?

21:27.554 --> 21:29.722
Beep, bom, bom!
Oh, my boychiks!

21:29.722 --> 21:31.658
Fun does not begin
to describe it.

21:31.658 --> 21:34.627
This is a day
that I will remember
for the rest of my life,

21:34.627 --> 21:37.364
even if I live
to be 100 years old.

21:37.364 --> 21:40.567
Which, by the way,
a lot of the men in my
family actually do,

21:40.567 --> 21:43.570
once they lay off the sweets
and the vengeful women.

21:46.138 --> 21:47.540
Thank you, boychiks.

21:50.543 --> 21:54.046
Ahoy! Well, well, well!

21:54.046 --> 21:56.549
Looks like someone's got
their sea legs back.

21:56.549 --> 21:58.551
Yeah,
I had some Captain Morgan's,

21:58.551 --> 22:00.453
a little gin, club soda.

22:00.453 --> 22:01.988
Feel a lot better.

22:01.988 --> 22:03.055
In fact.

22:05.758 --> 22:07.527
Come on down here, buddy.

22:07.527 --> 22:09.095
Turn and burn.

22:19.071 --> 22:20.139
Another summer, huh?

22:20.139 --> 22:22.208
Yeah.

22:22.208 --> 22:24.711
Think you'll be back
to Red Oaks next year?

22:24.711 --> 22:27.046
I barely know
what I'm doing next week,

22:27.046 --> 22:28.415
let alone next summer.

22:31.150 --> 22:33.786
It's gonna happen
for you, dude.

22:33.786 --> 22:34.987
I feel it.

22:34.987 --> 22:37.289
Maybe.

22:37.289 --> 22:38.891
I know one thing, though.

22:38.891 --> 22:40.960
It's not happening here
in Jersey.

22:40.960 --> 22:43.696
Hey, pizza's here.
Grabbed you a slice.

22:43.696 --> 22:47.099
That is why I love you.

22:47.099 --> 22:48.801
You do?

22:53.172 --> 22:55.742
Uh, yeah, sure.

22:55.742 --> 22:59.612
But, you know,
don't feel like you have
to say it back or anything.

23:06.085 --> 23:08.655
Eat your pizza.
Watch the sunset.

23:25.472 --> 23:27.073
You got enough room?

23:27.073 --> 23:28.941
Because your mom and I
could follow in the Volvo.

23:28.941 --> 23:29.776
No, I got it.

23:29.776 --> 23:33.480
Hey hey hey! There he is!

23:33.480 --> 23:35.482
Big man on campus!

23:35.482 --> 23:37.316
Hey, Mr. Myers, Mrs. Myers!

23:37.316 --> 23:39.586
Ah! Sorry! I mean Rosen.

23:39.586 --> 23:41.921
No, call us Sam and Judy.

23:41.921 --> 23:44.323
Actually, Mr. Myers
still works for me.

23:44.323 --> 23:47.393
All right. I'm sorry, I can't
really stay too long.

23:47.393 --> 23:48.928
I got my own packing
to do.

23:48.928 --> 23:52.164
- Oh.
- When do classes start?

23:52.164 --> 23:54.000
- Monday.
- Good for you.

23:54.000 --> 23:55.868
Very good.
Very proud of you.

23:55.868 --> 24:00.039
Thank you, Sam and Judy--
I mean Mr. Myers.

24:00.039 --> 24:02.509
- You're really doing this!
- I know. It's crazy.

24:02.509 --> 24:04.243
It's awesome!
I'm psyched for you.

24:04.243 --> 24:05.945
Making that leap.

24:05.945 --> 24:08.815
I'm psyched for you too,
Mr. Ivy League.

24:08.815 --> 24:11.383
Hey, you ever get
a hankering for
the campus life,

24:11.383 --> 24:13.620
you know my dorm room's
always open.

24:13.620 --> 24:15.622
Oh, definitely.
Soon as I'm settled,
I'm coming up.

24:15.622 --> 24:17.724
- Cool.
- Cool.

24:17.724 --> 24:19.526
- Cool.
- Cool.

24:19.526 --> 24:21.528
- Cool.
- Cool.

24:27.534 --> 24:28.835
Bye-bye.

24:32.905 --> 24:35.808
- What?
- Humor us.

24:35.808 --> 24:37.577
It's an emotional moment,

24:37.577 --> 24:39.245
especially for your ma.

24:39.245 --> 24:41.548
My baby.

24:45.184 --> 24:48.087
Mom, come on. It's not like
I'm moving to Guam.

24:54.293 --> 24:55.795
I love you.

25:00.099 --> 25:05.371
Honey, I know I can be
a pain in the ass sometimes,

25:05.371 --> 25:07.306
and I ride you too much,

25:07.306 --> 25:10.076
but I'm your dad.

25:10.076 --> 25:11.611
It's my job.

25:11.611 --> 25:12.879
I know.

25:12.879 --> 25:15.081
- I love you.
- I love you, too.

25:33.600 --> 25:35.201
Bye!

25:47.446 --> 25:50.216
- You okay?
- Yeah, I'm okay.

25:50.216 --> 25:52.151
Good.

25:52.151 --> 25:54.020
Because I'll lay you
even money

25:54.020 --> 25:55.722
that he's back
on one of our couches

25:55.722 --> 25:56.923
in the next few months.

25:56.923 --> 25:58.825
Oh, Sam.

25:58.825 --> 26:00.627
I wish I understood
what he was doing,

26:00.627 --> 26:03.730
but truth is
I haven't got a clue.

26:03.730 --> 26:04.964
Me neither.

26:06.699 --> 26:07.934
Think he's making a mistake?

26:07.934 --> 26:12.639
- I don't know.
- Me neither.

26:12.639 --> 26:15.174
Maybe we should let him.

27:06.158 --> 27:08.394
Hey, it's David.
I'm not here right now.

27:08.394 --> 27:10.096
Please leave a message
after the beep.

27:10.863 --> 27:12.732
Hey, it's me.

27:12.732 --> 27:14.600
I got your number
from your dad.

27:14.600 --> 27:16.703
I, um, I just wanted
to call and say that

27:16.703 --> 27:19.338
I watched your tape of Paris,
and I loved it.

27:19.338 --> 27:22.008
Uh, so...

27:22.008 --> 27:26.078
you can probably imagine things
are pretty crazy around here.

27:26.078 --> 27:28.715
My dad's lawyers are appealing.

27:28.715 --> 27:31.417
Oh, and believe it or not,

27:31.417 --> 27:34.954
I am taking a studio art class
at the New School.

27:34.954 --> 27:36.856
Yeah, I know.

27:36.856 --> 27:37.990
But my professor's
really great.

27:37.990 --> 27:39.726
And I'm enjoying it.

27:39.726 --> 27:41.627
So, um, I have to go,

27:41.627 --> 27:45.732
but... I don't know.
I just wanted
to call and say that

27:45.732 --> 27:48.534
I'm happy that you finally got
your place in the city.

27:48.534 --> 27:50.502
I bet you're really excited.

27:50.502 --> 27:55.274
Maybe we'll run
into each other sometime.

27:55.274 --> 27:56.876
Okay. Bye.

