* I've been in a cave *

29:00.606 --> 29:02.909
* For 40 days *

29:02.909 --> 29:05.144
* Only a spark *

29:05.144 --> 29:07.679
* To light my way *

29:07.679 --> 29:09.882
* I want to give out *

29:09.882 --> 29:12.251
* I want to give in *

29:12.251 --> 29:14.821
* This is our crime *

29:14.821 --> 29:16.923
* This is our sin *

29:16.923 --> 29:19.558
* But I still believe *

29:19.558 --> 29:21.861
* I still believe *

29:21.861 --> 29:24.230
* Through the pain *

29:24.230 --> 29:26.732
* And through the grief *

29:26.732 --> 29:28.935
* Through the lies *

29:28.935 --> 29:31.603
* Through the storms *

29:31.603 --> 29:33.605
* Through the cries *

29:33.605 --> 29:35.641
* And through the wars *

29:35.641 --> 29:37.509
* Oh, I still believe *

